grip: grip (GNOME CD Player and Ripper)
grip:
grip: Grip is a cd-player and cd-ripper for the GNOME desktop. It has the 
grip: ripping capabilities of cdparanoia builtin, but can also use external 
grip: rippers (such as cdda2wav). It also provides an automated frontend for 
grip: MP3 (and other audio format) encoders, letting you take a disc and 
grip: transform it easily straight into MP3s. Internet disc lookups are 
grip: supported for retrieving track information from disc database servers.
grip:
